### HTML
```html
<div class="circular-menu">
  <div class="menu-item">Item 1</div>
  <div class="menu-item">Item 2</div>
  <div class="menu-item">Item 3</div>
  <div class="menu-item">Item 4</div>
</div>
```

### CSS
```css
.circular-menu {
  position: relative;
  width: 100px;
  height: 100px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: #3498db;
  transition: width 0.3s, height 0.3s;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.menu-item {
  position: absolute;
  width: 80px;
  height: 40px;
  background: #2980b9;
  color: white;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  transition: transform 0.3s;
}

.menu-item:nth-child(1) { transform: translate(50%, -50%); }
.menu-item:nth-child(2) { transform: translate(100%, 0); }
.menu-item:nth-child(3) { transform: translate(50%, 50%); }
.menu-item:nth-child(4) { transform: translate(0, 100%); }

.circular-menu:hover {
  width: 200px;
  height: 200px;
}
```

### JavaScript
```javascript
